  "description": "<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.cctalk.com/gongkaike/151179119/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://f1.ct.hjfile.cn/pic/201402/568dd1db-d419-4111-b2cd-e334646b86f8.jpg\" /><br />\n\t</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #008000;\">沪江名师Giulia：Around the World: a Day in the Arctic<br />\n\t时间：3月13日（星期四）16:00 - 17:00<br />\n\t主讲老师：<span class=\"info_left\"><span class=\"info_left\"><span class=\"info_left\"><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/14058560\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Giulia</a></span></span></span><br />\n\t公开课地点：英语大厅（<a href=\"http://www.cctalk.com/download/\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk</a>）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.cctalk.com/gongkaike/151179119/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/f149ba0b08bd4f7d85f0034ae5a68a94.png\" /></span></a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">（本公开课只有注册用户才能参与，花<span style=\"color: #f00;\"><strong>5秒钟</strong></span>完成<strong><a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=yuer\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">注册吧&gt;&gt;&gt;</a></strong>）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t美女外教来了！英语大厅每周四下午 16:00-17:00 推出全新外教栏目，跟 Giulia 老师聊聊天。美国和意大利混血的 Giulia 老师说着一口标准流利的美语，并同时掌握意大利语、法语和西班牙语等多种语言。</p>\n<p>\n\tOn March 13th's 公开课, we'll be exploring one of the coldest areas on Earth: the Arctic Circle. We'll be looking at the different groups who live in the Arctic and brave its cold conditions, stories from the cultures, and explore the different ways they are able to survive.</p>\n<p>\n\tBring a hot cup of tea, you'll get cold just looking at pictures. Brrr!</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000;\"><strong>【讲师介绍】<br />\n\t</strong></span>Giulia 老师是美国意大利混血，母亲来自美国、父亲来自意大利。成长于欧洲和美国的她，已经在中国生活了近四年。她会说包括英语、意大利语、法语、西班牙语在内的多国语言，并正在努力学习中文。她很喜欢关于语言和文化的一切。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"white-space: normal;\">想加入Giulia老师的粉丝团吗？<a href=\"http://s.hujiang.com/topic/119134/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">请戳&gt;&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000;\">【课程大纲】<br />\n\t</span></strong>- Topic Introduction and Class Tips<br />\n\t- What do you know about the Arctic? Different areas of the Arctic, geographic introduction<br />\n\t- Who lives in the Arctic? A look at different groups and animals<br />\n\t- Culture of the indigenous groups in the Arctic<br />\n\t- How do they do it? A look at the daily life for someone living in the north pole<br />\n\t- Homework + Topic ideas: ways for you to get HuYuan and your chance to contribute what you would like Giulia to speak about</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201402/d8c8e5c03e5649efa20a6230df0bc72c.jpg\" /></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">本次课程完全免费，您需要做的就是：</span><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #f00;\"><strong>下载沪江全新语音学习软件--CCtalk&gt;&gt;点击下载</strong></span></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"width: 377px; height: 15px;\" /></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>请注意！参与本活动须使用沪江全新语音学习软件CCTalk，使用指南如下：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=eng2009\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">注册</span></a></strong>沪江网获得用户名（已是沪江用户的不必注册）；<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_gkkyd\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/fdac82641c98410a9fb1352dcdff5cd3.jpg\" /></a><br />\n\t2. 点击网址<a href=\"http://class.yeshj.com/zt/cctalk\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(7, 93, 179);\">http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk</span></a>下载CCtalk软件；<br />\n\t3. 软件安装结束后，输入沪江网的<b><span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\">用户名</span></b>和<span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><b>密码</b></span>